The paper discusses the use of machine vision in robotics, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also focuses on the challenges faced in machine vision, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of systematic literature review methodology suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and systems and control (cs.SY) as well.
